  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>刘小排</span> <span>2025-10-24 09:58</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p>实测开发实际产品，而不是用来画小球或者太阳系</p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b5ee2ad9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlFTMw4adAno3hOnibF4ibz4wkTOTAgGmCbkKYaJPp1mjWqRpefwJf91x6LKBCO6uR08JlFcjGqTNbDg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">大家好，我是刘小排。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">没想到快手也发布了编程模型。实测挺好的，推荐大家试试。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">省流版</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">亮点</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">-&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">速度飞快！</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">- 旗舰版</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">KAT-Coder-Pro V1 大约是claude-sonnet-4.0水平</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">-&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">有永久免费的版本&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">KAT-Coder-Air V1，足以完成小任务&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">- 做UI界面的挺实用，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">审美在线</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。下面可以看到实际案例</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">- 对Cline等VS Code编程插件的支持非常顺滑，不需要安装Claude Code来使用它。</span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">- 工具调用能力好，全程没有出现过工具调用错误。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">不足</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">- 不支持多模态</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">- 旗舰模型&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">KAT-Coder-Pro V1 虽然好用，但是如果不命中缓存的话，并不便宜。（好在赠送了免费额度，足够用一阵 ）</span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">- 编程能力不是最顶级的，稍微复杂的任务会出错。可以先使用Codex等等级模型做好Plan，再用KAT-Coder-Pro完成编码。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注册和使用</span></span></p>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\">到这里查看如何获取KEY。新用户赠送可用于<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">KAT-Coder-Pro V1的</span>2000万Token，足够玩好几天了。</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://www.streamlake.com/document/WANQING/me6ymdjrqv8lp4iq0o9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.streamlake.com/document/WANQING/me6ymdjrqv8lp4iq0o9</a></span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">文档中列出了多种使用方式，我建议新手朋友选择用Cline或Roo Code。</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">实测1：功能型AI产品，一次成功，功能完整，审美在线</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最近为了让我的 AI 编程的学员能学的更顺畅，我做了一个 AI 编程的脚手架，能够让习惯 Vibe coding 的用户更顺畅的开发自己的专业产品。</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">正好用这个新模型，来对我的脚手架进行功能新增的尝试，</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这次我在VS Code里使用 Cline 插件，用 key 的方式进行模型调用。 这是考虑到，很多刚接触编程的用户，安装Claude Code都是比较困难的。</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们先让他阅读代码，了解我的产品情况</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"1812\" data-imgfileid=\"100015649\" data-ratio=\"1.4777777777777779\" data-width=\"1226\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c3e5a29d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFTMw4adAno3hOnibF4ibz4wkVSxLxhlaVfosNagEuqkDOLMia9nITd7r6bNWoQHNr4l08EiaJzGRHU6A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"1926\" data-imgfileid=\"100015650\" data-ratio=\"1.512037037037037\" data-width=\"1274\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=296b7f47&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFTMw4adAno3hOnibF4ibz4wkbc7UqKz2QgtpKtOBZWa0XUYPNMicpjYetYhtwvMQXokqHZbvG772rAg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">看起来结果不错，而且速度飞快。调用工具没有明显的错误。看起来这个模型的Cline的配合也很不错。</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">接下来安排任务，让他进行真实的开发工作</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">下面是我的完整prompt</span></span></p>\n   <div>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">目标：在/demo/image界面，将生图功能修改为服装试穿功能</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">要求：用户上传人像照片+服装照片，生成人物试穿该服装的效果示例图片，需要保持人物的高度一致性还原，注意配置高质量的 prompt 且不要显示在客户端，页面精美符合试穿产品用户体验，代码示例如下：</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">curl -X POST <a href=\"https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/images/generations\" target=\"_blank\">https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3/images/generations</a> \\</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">-H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">-H \"Authorization: Bearer $ARK_API_KEY\" \\</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">-d '{</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">\"model\": \"doubao-seedream-4-0-250828\",</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">\"prompt\": \"Generate 3 images of a girl and a cow plushie happily riding a roller coaster in an amusement park, depicting morning, noon, and night.\",</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">\"image\": [\"<a href=\"https://ark-doc.tos-ap-southeast-1.bytepluses.com/doc_image/seedream4_imagesToimages_1.png\" target=\"_blank\">https://ark-doc.tos-ap-southeast-1.bytepluses.com/doc_image/seedream4_imagesToimages_1.png</a>\", \"<a href=\"https://ark-doc.tos-ap-southeast-1.bytepluses.com/doc_image/seedream4_imagesToimages_2.png\" target=\"_blank\">https://ark-doc.tos-ap-southeast-1.bytepluses.com/doc_image/seedream4_imagesToimages_2.png</a>\"],</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">\"sequential_image_generation\": \"auto\",</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">\"sequential_image_generation_options\": {</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">\"max_images\": 3</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">},</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">\"response_format\": \"url\",</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">\"size\": \"2K\",</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">\"stream\": true,</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">\"watermark\": true</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">}'</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">理解后和我讨论你的开发计划，确定没问题后再执行</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">ok，看他制定的开发计划，看起来是正确的</span></span></p>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"1966\" data-imgfileid=\"100015651\" data-ratio=\"1.6546296296296297\" data-width=\"1188\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17c5be99&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFTMw4adAno3hOnibF4ibz4wkhaVMicMUGhKC2zpV8ulCZDTK5dWv3ybyib6kOiaMkCCZhRm9cxBOngpHw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可以看出，和我沟通的要点比较精准，看起来有点聪明</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">继续对确认点一一回复</span></span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: italic;\">1.不需要自动裁剪，用户上传图片，走我们的存储逻辑，将r2链接发送到api就可以</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: italic;\">2.不需要特定参数，任务一致性通过 prompt 完成</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: italic;\">3.一次生成一张，不需要多张</span></span></p>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-style: italic;\">4.不需要不同的积分消耗</span></span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">改完了，看起来修改的文件是对的</span></span></p>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015652\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"3456\" data-height=\"2160\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=93275b11&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFTMw4adAno3hOnibF4ibz4wk4OJtj5Hib5lNibNBHpxNVbnkOC0vqsnlicZRKuUsjFHN1t3qmvNcpItxA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">看看页面，发现他对功能要求理解也正确</span></span></p>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"979\" data-imgfileid=\"100015648\" data-ratio=\"0.6027777777777777\" data-width=\"1625\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=24468e8a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFTMw4adAno3hOnibF4ibz4wkXzX7AgFs2RiaKJU9lxmJickicYOgFjfuBVvsnx2P2YAlnqCuRhgutDsdw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在需求基础上，准确的设计了，在生图页面添加了一个二级切换功能，实现的真实范围比我需求要求的范围要更加精准，并且实现的页面结构也在我的预期范围之外。</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">整体来说它做的页面效果满足了我的预期，不过表情符号乱出的情况，还是大模型的通病</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">接下来尝试，功能能否正常跑通</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"953\" data-imgfileid=\"100015654\" data-ratio=\"0.6111111111111112\" data-width=\"1560\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3890db6f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFTMw4adAno3hOnibF4ibz4wkJUsZ8ibRuHFkhM3bnAHQr5C5ibolWL4cNdyUzATemJ2r9CIav9IbJOPg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"982\" data-imgfileid=\"100015655\" data-ratio=\"0.6296296296296297\" data-width=\"1559\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=41b27a79&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFTMw4adAno3hOnibF4ibz4wk1kvws8Ns4HJ1ib1aY0ZibpmlRAwUVauMEysP78Ka3SQDu6ps2nQl0ezw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">完成的都很不错。</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">实测2：(复杂任务)订阅支付， 无法成功完成</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">接下来我们来测试更复杂的任务。让他完成本次任务产生的多语种衍生修改</span></span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">接下来，你需要帮助我处理多语种的实现，本次修改有些页面文案是硬编码状态，查看当前的多语种实现情况，进行多语种内容的完善</span></span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对Cline 的适配很丝滑，能动态查看模型修改的每一个细节</span></span></p>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"1138\" data-imgfileid=\"100015656\" data-ratio=\"0.6246524559777572\" data-width=\"1822\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=974289a1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2F607DKnuWzlFTMw4adAno3hOnibF4ibz4wkpoPqtUetxMLHzqgLFdBicCxHvrmNrVnvjjEwPEIjcbcouXCwRlZqWmQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">做对了，这个模型对项目进行多语种的处理很不错</span></span></p>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"956\" data-imgfileid=\"100015653\" data-ratio=\"0.4074074074074074\" data-width=\"2344\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=46e6f7b5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFTMw4adAno3hOnibF4ibz4wkGHaicxZa3MuLoGNvC6b1Xvf1oWRHD3GsljK1GVMZnkR7nANWfM6UaFQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最后尝试下，让他进行 creem 的支付功能的完整实现，目前脚手架支持用户进行产品的套餐购买，但是还没有实现套餐升级操套餐取消等功能。</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">现在让这个模型进行尝试试试看</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">下面是我的Prompt</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">背景：这是我做的对外销售的开发框架，能够帮助用户快速的在该代码基础上进行功能开发。 问题：当前 creem 支付方面，可以进行正常的付款，但还没有实现用户的套餐升级、订阅取消等功能</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">目标：参考 creem的api文档，设计开发计划，完整实现订阅相关的功能</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">api文档：</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">获取订阅-<a href=\"https://docs.creem.io/api-reference/endpoint/get-subscription\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.creem.io/api-reference/endpoint/get-subscription</a></span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">更新订阅-<a href=\"https://docs.creem.io/api-reference/endpoint/update-subscription\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.creem.io/api-reference/endpoint/update-subscription</a> 升级订阅-<a href=\"https://docs.creem.io/api-reference/endpoint/upgrade-subscription\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.creem.io/api-reference/endpoint/upgrade-subscription</a> 取消订阅-<a href=\"https://docs.creem.io/api-reference/endpoint/cancel-subscription\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.creem.io/api-reference/endpoint/cancel-subscription</a></span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">理解需求后，和我讨论开发计划</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在部分实现中，发现实现的内容和官方文档的api要求有出入，比如说发送接口不正确，本地的 planKey 没有映射到 Creem 的 product_id没有准确的将代码内容实现，在复杂任务的表现上还有待提高。</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;background-color: rgb(255, 104, 39);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">整体评价</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">整体体验下来，发现KAT-Coder-Pro 在智能体的适配上做的很好，与 Cline 的配合很丝滑，错误率也有优化</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在日常使用中，对界面的优化以及大范围的细碎任务处理，表现还不错，复杂难度任务还需要提高</span></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">目前有限时优惠，新用户注册即赠送KAT-Coder-Pro V1 2000 万 Tokens ； KAT-Coder-Air V1 的 API 将永久免费开放。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">期待你的反馈！</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"2247499321\">阅读原文</a></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=c6abff13&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzI1MTUxNzgxMA%3D%3D%26mid%3D2247499321%26idx%3D1%26sn%3D595f0936463290573a15e954d78a216c\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "快手新编程模型 KAT-Coder-Pro-V1 实测，速度快、UI 强、工具调用佳，但复杂任务仍有不足，提供免费额度。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "快手新编程模型 KAT-Coder-Pro-V1 实测，速度快、UI 强、工具调用佳，但复杂任务仍有不足，提供免费额度。",
  "summary": "文章对快手最新发布的编程模型 KAT-Coder-Pro-V1 和免费版 KAT-Coder-Air V1 进行了深度实测。Pro V1 模型在速度、UI 界面生成和工具调用方面表现出色，其能力被评估为与 Claude-Sonnet-4.0 相当，并能与 VS Code 插件（如 Cline）无缝集成。作者通过一个真实的产品开发任务（新增服装试穿功能）验证了其在功能实现和 UI 设计上的强大能力。然而，在处理更复杂的任务（如订阅支付功能集成）时，模型仍暴露出在理解 API 文档和准确实现方面的不足。文章强调了 Pro V1 的免费额度及 Air V1 的永久免费 API，为开发者提供了实用的使用建议和模型能力边界的清晰评估。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "KAT-Coder-Pro-V1 在日常编程任务中表现出色，尤其在 UI 生成和工具调用方面。",
      "explanation": "模型速度快，UI 审美在线，与 VS Code 插件 Cline 集成顺畅，工具调用无错误，能高效完成功能型 AI 产品的开发。"
    },
    {
      "point": "KAT-Coder-Pro-V1 在处理复杂业务逻辑和 API 集成时仍有局限性。",
      "explanation": "在订阅支付等复杂任务中，模型未能准确理解 API 文档并正确实现，表明其在复杂逻辑推理和精确代码实现方面尚需提升。"
    },
    {
      "point": "快手提供了免费额度与永久免费版本，降低了 AI 编程模型的试用门槛。",
      "explanation": "新用户可获得 2000 万 Token 的 Pro V1 免费额度，且 Air V1 模型 API 永久免费，鼓励开发者尝试和应用。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "实测开发实际产品，而不是用来画小球或者太阳系",
    "旗舰版 KAT-Coder-Pro V1 大约是 claude-sonnet-4.0 水平",
    "做 UI 界面的挺实用，审美在线。",
    "对 Cline 等 VS Code 编程插件的支持非常顺滑，不需要安装 Claude Code 来使用它。",
    "编程能力不是最顶级的，稍微复杂的任务会出错。可以先使用 Codex 等等级模型做好 Plan，再用 KAT-Coder-Pro 完成编码。"
  ],
